text Route_201_Text_TooSlow
{
    "Too slow!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Mentions_Idea
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: All right!\n"
    "Let's get moving to Prof. Rowan's lab."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Explains_Its_Fine
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "What?\n"
    "Don't go into grass, right?\l"
    "No worries! No problem!\p"
    "It doesn't matter that we don't have\n"
    "any Pokemon.\p"
    "Trust me on this one.\n"
    "I've got an idea!\p"
    "Now listen. You know how wild Pokemon\n"
    "jump out when you go into tall grass?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Explains_More
{
    "So, what you do is, you scoot over to\n"
    "the next patch of grass before any\l"
    "wild Pokemon can appear!\p"
    "If we just keep dashing, we can get to\n"
    "Sandgem Town without running into\l"
    "wild Pokemon!\p"
    "Ok, stick with me!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Talk_Before_Running
{
    "Ok, here goes!\p"
    "On your marks..."    
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Says_Hold
{
    "Hold it!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Tells_We_Are_Fools
{
    "Professor: You two don't seem to have\n"
    "any Pokemon between you?\p"
    "Then, what is the meaning of going into\n"
    "the tall grass?!\p"
    "{PLAYER}: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "Professor: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "...\n"
    "..."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Realize_Its_Rowan
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: Hey, {PLAYER}.\n"
    "This old guy...\p"
    "It's Prof. Rowan isn't it?\n"
    "What's he doing here...?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Thinks
{
    "Professor: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "They tried to go into the tall grass\n"
    "because they wanted Pokemon...\p"
    "Hmm...\n"
    "What to do...?\p"
    "Their world would surely change if\n"
    "they were to meet Pokemon...\p"
    "Is it right for me to put them on that\n"
    "path...?\p"
    "...\n"
    "..."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Asks
{
    "You two.\n"
    "You truly love Pokemon, do you?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Barry_Tells_You_Arent_Making_Sense
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: Whoa, hold\n"
    "You truly love Pokemon, do you?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Says_He_Didnt_Listen
{
    "Professor: Er-hem!\p"
    "I didn't quite catch that, so I will\n"
    "ask you again."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Also_Says_Yes
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: Me too!\n"
    "I love Pokemon, too!?\p"
    "Professor: I will ask you once again.\p"
    "You two.\n"
    "You truly love Pokemon, do you?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Continues
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: What?!\n"
    "You can ask a hundred times!\l"
    "The answer will never cange!\p"
    "We'll both answer a hundred times,\n"
    "we love Pokemon!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Asks
{
    "Right, {PLAYER}?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Joke_Is_Getting_Old
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: ...\n"
    "That joke's getting old!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Is_Worried
{
    "Professor: ...A Pair of reckless kids\n"
    "who foolishly try to enter tall grass\l"
    "without Pokemon of their own...?\p"
    "It worries me what people like that\n"
    "would do with Pokemon."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Agress_To_Give_Pokemon
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: ...Uh...\n"
    "Well, I, uh...\p"
    "...\n"
    "...\p"
    "Well, then forget about me, but give\n"
    "a Pokemon to my friend here!\p"
    "I mean, it was me who tried to go into\n"
    "the tall grass and all...\p"
    "Professor: !\p"
    "How big of you...\p"
    "Very, well, then!\n"
    "I will entrust you two with Pokemon!\p"
    "I apologize for putting you through\n"
    "that exercise.\p"
    "However!\p"
    "You must promise me that you will never\n"
    "recklessly endanger yourself again.\p"
    "Now, then...\p"
    "Hm?\n"
    "Now, where...?"    
}

